\par 
\par (Covering the period from 16th to 23rd March}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 1942) 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4682859 Note: }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 The figures in brackets refer to sources of information}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 
