\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 21)
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4682859 3. RUSSIA }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 
\par 
\par Admiration for Russian efforts continues}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 but doubts about the accuracy of their communiques grows.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 There is also increasing anxiety about the anticipated German Eastern offensive in the spring.
\par 
\par (1}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{
