\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4682859 4. LIBYA}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 
\par 
\par A slight increase of interest in Libya is reported}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 where it is thought that "another big effort by Rommel is imminent and inevitable".
\par 
\par (2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 10)
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4682859 5. U.S.A. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3870068 
\par 
\par It is increasingly believed that the U.S.A. is at last \'93getting a move on". Particularly in Australia. The news reels of Pearl Harbour are said to have "brought home to people}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15957576 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
